
Koonfurta Kalimantan (Indonesia: Kalimantan Selatan) waa gobolka Indonesia. Waxay ku taallaa Kalimantan, degaanka Indonesia ee Borneo. Magaalada caasimadda waa Banjarmasin. Dadweynaha Koonfurta Kalimantan waxaa lagu diiwaangeliyay in ka badan 3.625 milyan oo qof oo ah tirakoobkii 2010; [1] qiyaasta rasmiga ah ee rasmiga ah (bishii Janaayo 2014) waa 3,913,908.
Mid ka mid ah shan gobol oo Indonesia ah oo ku yaal Kalimantan, waxaa xuduud u leh Makassar Strait bari, Kalimantan galbeed iyo waqooyiga, Badda Java ee koonfurta, iyo Bariga Kalimantan ee waqooyiga.
